== License

Core Program: GPLv2
Scripts:      each script has its own license



== Required Packages

    python-setuptools
    python-vte or vte
    gettext
    zenity
    python-dev or python-devel
    python-distutils-extra
    wget
    git-core



== Installation

Please use the python setup tools to install.

	user@host# sudo ./setup.py install



== Usage

To run the GUI, use the following command:

	user@host# glzs

If it is the first time you run Lazyscripts, add "-a":

	user@host# glzs -a

To run with the last selection

	user@host# glzs --selection last_selection.ini

== Building a Debian package

    user@host# ./scripts/build_deb $tagname

    for example

    user@host# ./scripts/build_deb v0.2rc4



